e</a></li><li id="menu-item-62082" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-62082"><a href="/chi-siamo-autori/">Chi siamo</a></li><li id="menu-item-61925" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category current-post-ancestor current-menu-parent current-post-parent menu-item-has-children menu-item-61925"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/recensioni/">Opera</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-65488" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-65488"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/senza-categoria/">Foreign Readers</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-item-61927" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61927"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/concerti/">Concerti</a></li><li id="menu-item-61930" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61930"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/danza/">Danza</a></li><li id="menu-item-61933" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-61933"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/link/">Indirizzi utili</a></li><li id="menu-item-61928" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61928"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/interviste/">Interviste</a></li><li id="menu-item-61938" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-61938"><a href="#">Media</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-61940" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61940"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/cd-e-dvd/">Cd e Dvd</a></li><li id="menu-item-61941" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61941"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/libreria/">Libreria</a></li><li id="menu-item-61939" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-