o-10-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-puritani-al-teatro-real-di-madrid/' title='“I Puritani” al Teatro Real di Madrid'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Madrid, Teatro Real, 11 VII 2016 (I Puritani) 8" title="“I Puritani” al Teatro Real di Madrid" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li></ul> </aside></div></div></div><div id="footer" role="contentinfo"><div class="container"><div class="row-fluid"><div class="span6"><div class="copyright-info"> Associazione Culturale GB Opera<br/>Sede legale: vicolo Scala Santa 6 - 37129 Verona<br/>Codice fiscale: 93238110238 - info@gbopera.it<br/> Pubblicazione ai sensi della legge n. 62 del 07.03.2001.<br/>Copyright © 2008-2016</div></div><div class="span6"><div class="add-info"></div></div></div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">jQuery.noConflict()(function($){$(document).ready(function(){var $container=$('#blog-entry');$container.imagesLoaded(function(){$container.masonry({itemSelector:'.masonry-box',isAnimated:true,});});});});</script><script type="text/javascript">jQuery(document).ready(function(){var q2w3_sidebar_1_options={"sidebar":"q2w3-default-sidebar","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0,"stop_id":"","screen_max_width":0,"width_inherit":false,"widgets":['mainmenu-block-bg']};q2w3_sidebar(q2w3_sidebar_1_options);setInterval(function(){q2w3_sidebar(q2w3_sidebar_1_options);},1500);});</script><script type='text/javascript' src='h